<plot>A mesmerizing voyage into the world of early American artifacts. This sometimes trip like movie is a soothing blend of 19th century imagery and 21st digital editing effects. Hundreds of heart warming photographs from the country shops on the back roads of historic Brandywine Valley region near Philadelpia, Pennsylvania make this an authentic look a the simple things of life from an age now gone by.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?164270</url></doc>
